extends /components/layout.pug

block title
    title Academy of Learning | Home

block content 
    .container-fluid
    .mainpageheader.container-fluid
        .mainpageheaderform
            h1.white-text-md.text-center Funding Available for Those Who Qualify
            h2.white-text Canada&apos;s Largest Career College Network
            div
            iframe.afulliframe.iframe-full-height(title='Learnmoreframe' src='//form1.campuslogin.com/Academy_of_Learning_College/10400/Lead/AbbotsfordLangley.campuslogin?&style=//aolccbc.com/forms/transpform.css')
    .container-fluid
    .row
        .col-lg
            img(alt='Academy of Learning Career College logo' src='../images/Academt-of-Learning---final-logo-.webp' width='100%')
        .col
            h1.text-center ACADEMY OF LEARNING CAREER COLLEGE
            h2.text-center.orange-text Canada&apos;s Largest Career College Network.
            p.text-center
                | At Academy of Learning, we attribute our rapid growth to our success in identifying and filling the gap between the formal education currently available in Canada and the realities of the working world. We provide learners the solutions
                | they need by offering customized, convenient and affordable programs.
            p.text-center
                | In today&apos;s business world, where quality training is not only important but essential to career success, Academy of Learning Career College stands out as a training provider relied on by students, employers and government agencies. No
                | other private post-secondary college can match the variety of programs that Academy of Learning Career College offers. Students can choose from over 30 diploma and certificate programs offered at Academy of Learning Career College.
            p &nbsp;
            p.text-center
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.orange-btn(href='aboutus.html' role='button') ABOUT AOLCC
    section
        .container-fluid
        .row
            .col-lg-12.mb-4.mt-2.text-center
                h2 FEATURES
    .container-fluid
        .row
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 LEARN AT YOUR OWN PACE
                p
                    | Our campuses provide a relaxing atmosphere where you can learn at your own pace. The features of our Integrated Learning System&reg; allow for flexibility in your daily schedule. You can finish your program quickly to get into the
                    | job market faster.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 JOB PLACEMENT
                p
                    | Diploma programs feature real-world job placement so you&apos;re job-ready at graduation. A number of our adult learners are hired by their placement sites.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 PRACTICAL EXPERIENCE
                p
                    | Many of our programs feature a practical component in which learners gain valuable experience with actual clients.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 SHORT, EFFECTIVE COURSES
                p
                    | We offer short programs, so you can earn your Diploma or Certificate in just 4-12 months instead of the conventional 2-4 years at a Community College or University. This gives you the financial flexibility to get into the workforce
                    | sooner, instead of being tied to a Community College or University for several years.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 FLEXIBLE SCHEDULING
                p
                    | Work / Life balance is important. Don&apos;t give up on your dream of a better career to help you and your family. Our flexible hours and online learning allow you to earn a Diploma or Certificate with minimal disruption to your daily schedule.
                    | You&apos;ll be able to balance your education with your employment and your family. With our continuous enrolment, it is never too late for you to start.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 DIPLOMA AND CERTIFICATE PROGRAMS
                p
                    | We offer over 30 Diploma and Certificate programs for you to choose from. For one-on-one support, Learning Coaches are available at all times to provide personalized guidance and assistance to help you succeed!
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 HANDS-ON TRAINING
                p
                    | Audio, visual, online and rich media instructions are used to explain concepts and guide learners through initial skill-based applications. Hands-on tasks give students an opportunity to apply skills to &ldquo;real life&rdquo; situations. We help
                    | you master the subject matter before moving onto the next lesson.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 SAFE, COMFORTABLE LEARNING ENVIRONMENT
                p
                    | There&apos;s no intimidating classroom atmosphere or competition! We ensure a comfortable, safe and friendly learning environment for all adult learners. If you need to miss a lesson, you can take the same lesson at another time. With ILS
                    | and online learning you&apos;ll never miss an assignment or lesson.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                h3 INTEGRATED LEARNING SYSTEM (ILS)
                p
                    | Course materials and instructions provide an all-encompassing learning experience using multi-sensory learning styles and preferences through student workbooks, media presentations, and hands-on activities.
        .row
            // Testemonials
            // <div w3-include-html="feedback.php">
            // Testemonials
    .container-fluid
        .row
            .text-center.col-md-8.col-12.mx-auto
                h1.orange-text DEDICATED TO QUALITY
                p
                    | Our programs are conceived and developed with learners&apos; needs and ease of use in mind. At Academy of Learning Career College, Canada&apos;s largest career college network, our training program will set you up for success. Learn more about
                    | our world-class Integrated Learning System (ILS).
    .position-images.wpb_single_image.center
        img(alt='Academy of Learning Integrated Learning System' src='/images/ils.webp')
    .orange.text-center.banner
        a.white-text-md(href='programs/') We have more than 30+ programs. EXPLORE &gt;
    .banner(style='height: 10px;')
    .inline-block
        .sixtypcthz
            img.sixtypcthz(alt='Map of Campuses on an iMac' src='/images/imac-final.webp')
        .fiftypcthz.float-right
            h1 50+ CAMPUSES ACROSS CANADA.
            h2
                | As a Canadian Owned and Operated Company, we are proud to deliver quality Education to our fellow Canadians.
            hr
            p
                | With 50+ campuses across Canada we are Canada&apos;s largest career college. As a Canadian owned and operated company, we understand the requirements of Canadian learners and tailor our curriculum and learning outcomes for the realities of
                | the Canadian job market.
            .btn
                a(href='locations/') FIND A LOCATION NEAR YOU
    .grey-bg.text-center.white-text
        p
            b CALL US TODAY AT 604-855-3315
        p
            | WE STRIVE TO PROVIDE OUR ADULT LEARNERS WITH THE HIGHEST QUALITY IN EDUCATION, CURRICULUM, SERVICE AND TECHNOLOGY
        .row
            .col-sm-4.col-auto.mx-auto
                a.btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-success.orange-btn(href='ils.html' title='') LEARN MORE
    .container-fluid(style='height: 600px;')
        .row.afulliframe
            .row.text-center
            h2 Request more info
            .row.text-center
                iframe.moreinfoform(title='moreinfoform' src='//form1.campuslogin.com/Academy_of_Learning_College/10400/Lead/AbbotsfordLangley.campuslogin?&style=//aolccbc.com/forms/clform.css')
            .row.mt-2
    include /components/promisebar.html